I don’t know if you got it to work yet, because I am too lazy to read the topic, but if you haven’t, try this…

“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java

In the part above, the “06” is the update of the Java JDK that you have. If you downloaded the JDK in the past few days, you should try replacing the “6” with a “9”.
